# Slot Pilot — 4 Core Pro Features Implementation

Upgrade Slot Pilot from a basic visa site to a full-service Concierge & Intelligence platform by adding Mistake Analysis, Employee Command Dashboard, Travel Net reviews, and Concierge Stays booking.

## Proposed Changes

### Firestore Schema Additions

The `posts` collection documents will be extended with optional fields:

| Field | Type | Used By |
|---|---|---|
| `rejectionInsights` | `{ mistakes: [{ text, explanation, proTip }] }` | Mistake Analysis |
| `travelReview` | `{ rating, pros: [], cons: [], hiddenGems: [] }` | Travel Net |
| `verified` | `boolean` | Verified badge |
| `verifiedAt` | `Timestamp` | Badge timestamp |
| `verifiedBy` | `string` | Employee who verified |

New collection: **`employee_tasks`**

| Field | Type | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `type` | `"secure_room"` | Task type |
| `postId` | `string` | Reference to stays post |
| `postTitle` | `string` | Post headline |
| `landlordContact` | `string` | From post content |
| `userRequest` | `string` | "Secure the room" |
| `requestedBy` | `string` | User identifier |
| `status` | `"pending" / "in_progress" / "done"` | Task status |
| `createdAt` | `Timestamp` | Auto timestamp |

